reviewText: Now my boys can watch without using my old worn out vhs tapes. Showed up in 2 days 10 before it was expected
If you were a skater in the 80's, then you remember these moves and these movies.  And, you're probably ~40 years old now, have a job, and can afford this box set.  So order already!

Anyone who skated in the 80's remember's these videos.  They are awesome.  Its amazing how the so many tricks of today all started from these guys.  Video's are a little corny, but still fun to watch.  My kids now like them as well.
This 6 pack is exactly as advertised. It is all the great old Powell Peralta videos and you will not be disappointed.
